 <span data-ttu-id="2bb02-103">您可以處理<xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipProvider.ValidatingPassword>事件，以便驗證密碼的格式和成員資格使用者的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bb02-103">You can handle the <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipProvider.ValidatingPassword> event to validate password formats and values for membership users.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="2bb02-104">您可以取消目前<xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipProvider.CreateUser%2A>， <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipProvider.ChangePassword%2A>，或<xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipProvider.ResetPassword%2A>藉由設定動作<xref:System.Web.Security.ValidatePasswordEventArgs.Cancel%2A>屬性設`true`期間<xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipProvider.ValidatingPassword>事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bb02-104">You can cancel the current <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipProvider.CreateUser%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipProvider.ChangePassword%2A>, or <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipProvider.ResetPassword%2A> action by setting the <xref:System.Web.Security.ValidatePasswordEventArgs.Cancel%2A> property to `true` during the <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipProvider.ValidatingPassword> event.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="2bb02-105">如果您藉由設定取消目前的動作<xref:System.Web.Security.ValidatePasswordEventArgs.Cancel%2A>屬性，以`true`，您可以設定<xref:System.Web.Security.ValidatePasswordEventArgs.FailureInformation%2A>描述密碼驗證失敗的原因的例外狀況的屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bb02-105">If you cancel the current action by setting the <xref:System.Web.Security.ValidatePasswordEventArgs.Cancel%2A> property to `true`, you can set the <xref:System.Web.Security.ValidatePasswordEventArgs.FailureInformation%2A> property to an exception that describes the reason for the password-validation failure.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bb02-106">呼叫方法會擲回例外狀況，<xref:System.Web.Security.ValidatePasswordEventArgs.FailureInformation%2A>屬性設定為。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bb02-106">The calling method will throw the exception that the <xref:System.Web.Security.ValidatePasswordEventArgs.FailureInformation%2A> property is set to.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2bb02-107">如果<xref:System.Web.Security.ValidatePasswordEventArgs.FailureInformation%2A>屬性是`null`，呼叫端將會擲回一般的密碼驗證失敗例外狀況。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2bb02-107">If the <xref:System.Web.Security.ValidatePasswordEventArgs.FailureInformation%2A> property is `null`, the caller will throw a generic password-validation failure exception.</span></span>  
  
   
  
